The following is a list of awards and nominations received by American actor [[Gene Hackman]]. For his role in ''[[The French Connection (film)|The French Connection]]'', he won an [[Academy Award for Best Supporting Actor|Academy Award]], a [[BAFTA Award for Best Actor in a Leading Role|BAFTA Award]], and a [[Golden Globe Award for Best Actor&nbsp;– Motion Picture Drama|Golden Globe]] for Best Actor. He won all three awards again for his role in ''[[Unforgiven]]''. In 2003, he won the [[Golden Globe Cecil B. DeMille Award|Cecil B. DeMille Award]].

